tswitem.name: Rampant Augment Resonator
tswitem.tooltip:
Rampant Augment Resonator
An unattuned support augment.
Resonating this augment to an active ability will increase the number of targets affected by 1/ 2/ 3/ 4/ 5. Resonating this augment to a single target ability has no effect.
To attune this augment, place it in the assembly window with:
  • 2 Attuned Curing Augment Resonators
  • 30 Pure wheel runes
  • 30 Pure metal
